    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218640/extras/c42cecb072c53c9f93a5b0bc4902bd8f.avif?t=1691200971\" width=630 height=214 /></span><br><br>盔甲战衣在身，尖矛利盾在手。只因邪恶势力再次祸及天下。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏概要</h2><br><br>龙血骑士是一款残酷无情、极其困难的2D动作平台类游戏，也有部分银河恶魔城的风格。使用双摇杆，提供复杂精细、极具挑战的操作体验。战斗需要处处小心，却又极富冲击力；需要极快决定策略，加以执行。你会一死再死，但只要你从每次战斗中积累经验，所有敌人都终会倒下。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218640/extras/be1765bc32720ea3da502d7c1f99711d.avif?t=1691200971\" width=630 height=268 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与令人窒息的强大敌人对峙</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218640/extras/8fdeded6997175b494be088c37f2b36a.avif?t=1691200971\" width=630 height=192 /></span><br><br>在你的旅程中，遭遇愈发强大和可怖的怪兽。每个敌人都有别具一格的优势和弱点，而你需要尊重优势、利用弱点。骑士必须时时谨慎方能在战场中存活，而炉火纯青者则能以一敌百。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218640/extras/bc8e751760d07b4593faca6af5a7764b.avif?t=1691200971\" width=630 height=192 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >史诗般的首领战</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218640/extras/78f13c7d494b547f041989228622e022.avif?t=1691200971\" width=630 height=192 /></span><br><br>首领战注定是残酷且充满挑战的。研究你的敌人，培养适应力，如果拥有足够的韧性和技巧，也许最强大的敌人也会败下阵来。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218640/extras/ea509782d35ca54c2a634a51c3ce6477.avif?t=1691200971\" width=630 height=376 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >为骑士赋能</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218640/extras/c12582ebe0bf4df463c8325fabebfa50.avif?t=1691200971\" width=630 height=192 /></span><br><br>攻破最强大的敌人，突破人类极限，解锁你的龙族超能。寻求盟友们的帮助，他们也许略知一二。每当解锁新技能、升级护甲时，你探索环境、摧毁敌人的能力就会增强一分。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218640/extras/4e12b19118dddc45b47327b09e18b503.avif?t=1691200971\" width=630 height=192 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事梗概</h2><br><br>故事开始于龙血王国，在这里人类与龙族和平共存。但如今暗影遮蔽大地，怪物肆意横行。龙血骑士们曾在伟大战争时期扭转战局，而当下也在勉强支撑着王国的防卫。<br><br>故事讲述一名只身行动的龙血骑士，为了夺回落入敌手的要塞而战。探索巨大城堡，战胜种种威胁，揭开遍布大地的敌人的神秘面纱。",
